com.cisco.pxgrid.util

Class GenericMessageBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cisco.pxgrid.util.GenericMessageBuilder

  • public abstract class GenericMessageBuilder
extends Object
    A generic message builder for the given capability name and operation name

    Sample Usage:

    GenericMessageBuilder builder = GenericMessageBuilder.notificationBuilder("topic-name", "oper-name");

    GenericMessageBuilder builder = GenericMessageBuilder.requestBuilder("topic-name", "oper-name");

    GenericMessageBuilder builder = GenericMessageBuilder.responseBuilder("topic-name", "oper-name");

    byte[] rawContent;

    GenericMessage message = builder.addRawContent(rawContent, "tag-01", "tag-02").build();

    String plainTextContent;

    GenericMessage message = builder.addPlainTextContent(plainTextContent, "tag-01", "tag-02").build();

    Object pxGridModelContent;

    GenericMessage message = builder.addPxGridModelContent(pxGridModelContent, "tag-01", "tag-02").build();

    BaseError error;

    GenericMessage message = builder.setError(error).build();

    Author:
    anto
